## **Education (Class Reminder)**

“Write a reminder for students about tomorrow’s online class.”

Role: You are a science teacher at a private school.
Context: You need to remind 6th grade students about tomorrow’s mandatory online science class.
Action: Write a friendly email reminder (maximum 50 words) informing students that the class will be held tomorrow from 1 PM to 2 PM.
If students face any issues or cannot attend, they should email the reason to mikeo@gmail.com.
Audience: 6th grade students
Channel: Email
Tone: Friendly and encouraging
Constraints: Simple, age-appropriate language
